TextBody:
Hey Michael,

Thank you for meeting with us today. Unfortunately, it looks like SA was erroring due to a misconfigured path in SAM for the host in question so we were unable to recover the deletion you were looking for. However, we corrected this issue for this SDC-FILESRVR50 by adding the rest of the directory to the path:
